001package org.consensusj.bitcoin.json.pojo;
002
003import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonCreator;
004import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
005
006/**
007 * Response object for {@code createwallet} and {@code loadwallet}
008 */
009public class LoadWalletResult {
010      private final String name;
011      private final String warning;
012
013
014    @JsonCreator
015    public LoadWalletResult(@JsonProperty("name") String name, @JsonProperty("warning") String warning) {
016        this.name = name;
017        this.warning = warning;
018    }
019
020    public String getName() {
021        return name;
022    }
023
024    public String getWarning() {
025        return warning;
026    }
027}
